Everything
from words to weather

00:17.100 --> 00:21.000
<i>We'll discover them</i>

00:21.000 --> 00:24.100
Together

00:24.100 --> 00:26.700
<i>- [Dog] Woof!</i>
<i>- [Woman] Because he's still sick, Ma.</i>

00:26.700 --> 00:29.300
- He can't keep anything down,
and he's runnin' a temperature.
- [Singing Continues]

00:29.300 --> 00:33.000
What am I supposed to do?
My shift starts in a half an hour.

00:33.000 --> 00:36.000
<i>Every day's a new beginning</i>
<i>All your friends are here and grinning</i>

00:36.000 --> 00:38.800
- 'Cause it's <i>Smile Time</i>
