- [Singing Continues, Indistinct]

00:44.100 --> 00:47.400
Okay, Tommy.
You know what to do.

00:47.400 --> 00:51.300
<i>Tommy, you should</i>
<i>never break a promise.</i>

00:51.300 --> 00:55.300
You don't wanna
be a bad apple, do you? Come on.

00:55.500 --> 00:57.900
<i>You know</i> Smile Time <i>isn't free.</i>

00:57.900 --> 01:00.600
Now, get over here and touch it.

01:00.600 --> 01:04.900
<i>All your friends are here and grinning</i>
<i>'cause it's</i> Smile Time

01:04.900 --> 01:08.500
That's it, Tommy.
Come on.

01:08.500 --> 01:11.300
- Touch it.
- [Singing Continues, Indistinct]

01:11.300 --> 01:14.700
Oh! Oh! Ah.

01:14.700 --> 01:19.200
<i>That's it. Oh, yeah.</i>
<i>Good boy, Tommy.</i>

01:21.300 --> 01:23.200
Oh. Ah.

01:25.100 --> 01:28.500
<i>Okay, Tommy.</i>
<i>Grammy's gonna be here in a few hours.</i>

01:28.500 --> 01:31.300
<i>And listen. I don't want you</i>
<i>watching that crap all day long.</i>

01:31.300 --> 01:35.200
<i>Because it's</i> Smile Time That's right!
