<i>[Muffled Clanking]</i>

11:23.000 --> 11:25.900
<i>[Rumbling Continues]</i>

11:37.000 --> 11:41.300
<i>- [Clanking]</i>
<i>- [Electrical Arcing]</i>

12:20.500 --> 12:22.900
[Gasping]

12:25.000 --> 12:27.800
<i>[Rumbling]</i>

12:28.900 --> 12:31.900
[Raspy Voice]
You shouldn't...

12:31.900 --> 12:34.400
be here.

