- Fred...

39:40.400 --> 39:43.200
Haven't you been
sensing anything lately?

39:43.200 --> 39:46.000
About me?
Coming from me?

39:46.000 --> 39:51.500
Didn't occur to you
that something might've changed...

39:51.500 --> 39:54.900
that I'm looking at you
in a different...

39:54.900 --> 39:57.700
l... Oh, screw it.

